Package backEnd

Enum Priorities

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Priorities>
      • backEnd.Priorities
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Priorities>
    public enum Priorities
extends java.lang.Enum<Priorities>
    This Priorities enum contains several options that the user can pick to signify when they should get their task done. It also contains several helper methods that mostly help convert string priorities to the enum type.
    Author:
    Evan Nadelbach
